pr_title: Enhance support for `ALTER TABLE` and `ALTER VIEW` in PostgreSQL
pr_body:
Ref #17848 
Sub-issue of  #14015

Changes proposed in this pull request:
- `ALTER TABLE` was already partially supported, this
PR enhances that support.
